<Layout title="Men's Shoe Size Conversion Chart: US, UK, EU, CM | Classic Menswear Chronicle">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Men's Shoe Size Conversion Chart: US, UK, EU, and CM</h1>
  <p class="mb-8">Navigate international shoe sizes with ease using our comprehensive conversion chart. Whether you're shopping for Italian leather shoes or British brogues, this guide will help you find the perfect fit in US, UK, EU, and centimeter measurements.</p>
  
  <ShoeSizeChart />
  
  <div class="mt-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">How to Measure Your Foot</h2>
    <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2">
      <li>Place a piece of paper on a hard floor against a wall.</li>
      <li>Stand on the paper with your heel against the wall.</li>
      <li>Mark the longest part of your foot on the paper.</li>
      <li>Measure the distance from the wall to the mark in centimeters.</li>
      <li>Add 0.5cm to your measurement for wiggle room.</li>
    </ol>
  </div>
  
  <p class="mt-8 text-gray-600">Note: Different brands may have slight variations in sizing. When in doubt, refer to the brand's specific size chart or try on shoes before purchasing.</p>
</Layout>